sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Shopper
    participant Web as Browser SPA
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Cart as Cart Service
    participant Pay as Payment Gateway
    participant Inv as Inventory Service
    participant DB as Orders Database

    User->>Web: Click "Place order"
    Web->>GW: POST /checkout (session cookie)
    GW->>Auth: Validate session token
    Auth->>Auth: Decode and verify JWT signature
    Auth-->>GW: 200 principal + granted scopes
    GW->>Cart: Fetch active cart for user
    Cart->>DB: SELECT items WHERE cart_id = ?
    DB-->>Cart: 14 line items returned
    Cart-->>GW: Cart snapshot with subtotal
    GW->>Inv: Reserve stock for line items
    Inv->>Inv: Lock rows and decrement counts
    Inv-->>GW: Reservation token (5 min TTL)
    GW->>Pay: Authorize charge for $248.19
    Pay->>Pay: Run fraud heuristics scoring
    Pay-->>GW: Authorization approved
    GW->>DB: INSERT order (status = pending)
    DB-->>GW: order_id 90871 committed
    GW->>Inv: Commit stock reservation
    Inv-->>GW: Stock permanently committed
    GW-->>Web: 201 Created order 90871
    Web-->>User: Show confirmation page